Vote. Become a pollworker if you can. Learn how elections work in your community.

@jonahb It should work well for that, with two caveats:

- For good performance, you'd want the antennas arranged in at least a 50cm or so radius circle, which is a tight fit for some cars.

- 121.5 ELTs are becoming obsolete, so as SAR capabilities go, it's less important than it was.
